channel.title: Bizarre suicide attempt claims 2 lives in Chile
channel.description:
A suicide in Chile has claimed two lives by accident, is what the Chilean Police said. In Antofogasta, in northern Chile, a woman named Josefina Venizela, jumped off of the 12th floor of an office building. She landed on the 56 years old Luisa Almendares, mother of 4 and cleaning lady, who was just taking out the trash, 40 minutes before her shift would've ended.
Source (dutch): [url=http://frontpage.fok.nl/nieuws/387362/1/1/50/bizarre-zelfmoord-eist-twee-levens-in-chili.html]http://frontpage.fok.nl/nieuws/387362/1/1/50/bizarre-zelfmoord-eist-twee-levens-in-chili.html[/url] I guess that wasn't her lucky day :rolleyes:
